EN:This package needs special handling because it contains fragile items.

ZH:他们在包裹上贴了许多邮票，以确保它可以快速送达。
EN:They attached many stamps to the package to ensure it would be delivered quickly.

ZH:邮递员把包裹放在门口，然后匆匆跑回邮车。
